{"tid":2324632,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"考閱過去 3000 年各國歷史，終於搵到點解搣時潘要叫 MissPunPun","createTime":"2020-12-14T05:27:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T02:10:12.000Z","uid":36383,"like":28,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5718938639637d30bf70fe3bf7d2fe309632e15c","tid":2324632,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T05:27:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%BD%98%E6%BD%98_(%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25BD%2598%25E6%25BD%2598_%28%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%29&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725Kd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=37ed5f25\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%BD%98%E6%BD%98_(%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC)</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">潘潘泛指沒有固定客戶的日本妓女。</span>那些有固定客戶被美軍包養的妓女則被稱為「安麗」，英文「ONLY」的諧音，也被稱為「Only -San」。<br />\n<br />\n那些專門服務歐美人的潘潘也被稱為「洋潘潘」。<br />\n<br />\n那些專門服務白人的潘潘也被稱為「白潘潘」、「山羊潘潘」（因為白人像山羊一樣白）<br />\n<br />\n那些專門服務黑人的潘潘也被稱為「黒潘潘」<br />\n<br />\nsource from Wiki <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我潘紀念日本戰後女權受打壓，自名PunPun"},{"pid":"903a4a62b4c6ec774197fcd662638b562923418d","tid":2324632,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T05:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黑潘潘"},{"pid":"eff814240c6d8a6373a14b79dcea0bf9ed597b04","tid":2324632,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T05:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 牛肺潘潘"},{"pid":"db90accaf8bc94999cccba3da502b49b68d2d3cb","tid":2324632,"uid":36297,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T05:30:36.000Z","msg":"咪屈我pun"},{"pid":"a4590372afd1fa0830e552fa7f0db47c02e71887","tid":2324632,"uid":36383,"l